INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (796,127,'_highlight_subtitle','How SMDCs Red Residences is Shaping the Citys Next Creative Community');
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (797,127,'_highlight_sub_description','Makati is changingbut not in the places you expect. While the usual districts are still defined by glass towers and boardroom bustle');
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (798,127,'_highlight_news','Along the edges of Chino Roces Avenue, the citys next creative community is emergingbuilt by the everyday choices of people who want to live, work, and create on their own terms.\r\n<br><br>\r\nCentral to this subtle but significant shift is Red Residences by SM Development Corporation (SMDC). Rather than simply occupying a trendy address, Red Residences is actively helping shape it  creating a thoughtfully curated living environment that aligns deeply with its residents values of creativity, community, and purposeful urban life.\r\n<br><br>\r\nEach design choice at Red is deliberate. Thoughtfully sized balconies provide private outdoor spaces essential for reflection and clarity, while a serene Sunset Lounge offers a quiet venue to unwind, plan, or connect meaningfully with neighbors. Carefully landscaped gardens invite moments of stillness and community connection amidst Makatis pace.\r\n<br><br>\r\nBut Red isnt just about whats inside the building. Its about being part of something bigger. SMDC has planted Red Residences in a real, growing neighborhood  surrounded by independent galleries, coffee shops, creative studios, and local businesses that give Chino Roces its pulse. Its not trying to recreate culture  its choosing to live in the middle of it.  In a city full of generic towers, this is what real, rooted urban living looks like.\r\n<br><br>\r\nPeople who choose to live want real value: good design, a sense of community, and a place where connections actually matter. At Red Residences, it means living somewhere that feels personal, thoughtful, and grounded in everyday meaning.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn this quieter yet impactful evolution of Makati, Red Residences doesnt merely participate  it quietly leads the way.');
