INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (806,130,'_highlight_subtitle','SMDCs Established Communities Define Commitment');
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (807,130,'_highlight_sub_description','SMDC has established one of the most extensive portfolios of completed residential communities in the country');
INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (808,130,'_highlight_news','Scale with Delivery\r\n<br><br>\r\nSMDCs development logic is defined not only by volume, but by consistency. Its communities form a working urban network across Metro Manila, Cavite, Laguna, Tagaytay, Bulacan, Pampanga, Tarlac, Iloilo, Bacolod, CDO, and Davaoregions chosen for both population growth and infrastructure access. SMDC builds communities in a way thats consistent, well-planned, and supported by a system that few competitors can replicate.\r\n<br><br><br>\r\nUrban Integration as Strategy\r\n<br><br>\r\nSMDCs access to the SM ecosystem allows its developments to serve as connected, self-sustaining communities from day one. Many are co-located with SM malls, transport terminals, groceries, and essential servicesgiving residents immediate access to daily needs.\r\n<br><br><br>\r\nThe result: communities that function independently, with high occupancy, active leasing, and strong retail activity. Properties such as Shore Residences, Light Residences, and Trees Residences are no longer launch storiesthey are part of the lived city.\r\n<br><br>\r\nWhat defines SMDC is not the promise to buildbut the ability to activate and sustain communities over time, says Grace Sta. Ana, Executive Vice President and Head of Core Operations. We operate at national scale, and yet the output is localreal homes in real neighborhoods, occupied and growing.\r\n<br><br>\r\nJessica Sy, Vice President and Head of Design, Innovation, and Strategy, adds: At SMDC, we design with delivery in mind. A development only becomes meaningful when people are actually living and thriving in itwhen the lights are on, the shops are open, and the community begins to grow. Thats when a project becomes real.\r\n<br><br><br>\r\nRed Residences: A Case of Ready Urban Living\r\n<br><br>\r\nRed Residences in Chino Roces, Makati, is one of SMDCs latest move-in-ready developments. Strategically located near transport and creative-commercial zones, the property has already completed turnover and is home to early residents. With compact units, efficient amenities, and walkability to Makatis business corridors, it reflects SMDCs refined approach to high-density, livable design.\r\n<br><br>\r\nIn todays market, what matters isnt just whats promisedits whats already built, lived in, and working. SMDC continues to deliver real homes in real communities, ready for life today.');
